Advance width of hmtx and CFF table should be the same (tolerance 2 units).

This is a TrueType font. This test is only for CFF.

Mukta ExtraLight Regular (Mukta-ExtraLight.ttf)

name

MS NID 16/17

MS NID 16 + NID 17 should match NID 1 (+2).
Otherwise cross platform compatibility does not work between Mac (uses NID 16+17) and Windows (uses NID 1+2). (Jan 2019)

NID 16 'Mukta' + 'Space' + NID 17 'ExtraLight' = NID 1 'Mukta ExtraLight'.

Mac NID 6

Mac NID 6, PostScript Name check for illegal characters.
Monotype uses NID 6 for creating CSS classes for their demo HTML. The following characters cause issues in the CSS code: '
, , , &, _, [, ], (, ), {, }, <, >, /, \, %'

NID 6 is 'Mukta-Light', Everything looks good.

Mukta Light Regular (Mukta-Light.ttf)

name

MS NID 16/17

MS NID 16 + NID 17 should match NID 1 (+2).
Otherwise cross platform compatibility does not work between Mac (uses NID 16+17) and Windows (uses NID 1+2). (Jan 2019)

NID 16 'Mukta' + 'Space' + NID 17 'Light' = NID 1 'Mukta Light'.

Pass

Mukta Medium Regular (Mukta-Medium.ttf)

name

Mac NID 6

Mac NID 6, PostScript Name check for illegal characters.
Monotype uses NID 6 for creating CSS classes for their demo HTML. The following characters cause issues in the CSS code: '
, , , &, _, [, ], (, ), {, }, <, >, /, \, %'

NID 6 is 'Mukta-Medium', Everything looks good.

Pass

Mukta Medium Regular (Mukta-Medium.ttf)

name

MS NID 16/17

MS NID 16 + NID 17 should match NID 1 (+2).
Otherwise cross platform compatibility does not work between Mac (uses NID 16+17) and Windows (uses NID 1+2). (Jan 2019)

NID 16 'Mukta' + 'Space' + NID 17 'Medium' = NID 1 'Mukta Medium'.

Mukta SemiBold Regular (Mukta-SemiBold.ttf)

name

MS NID 6

MS NID 6, PostScript Name check for illegal characters.
Monotype uses NID 6 for creating CSS classes for their demo HTML. The following characters cause issues in the CSS code: '
, , , &, _, [, ], (, ), {, }, <, >, /, \, %'

NID 6 is 'Mukta-SemiBold', Everything looks good.

Pass

NID 6 is 'Mukta-SemiBold', Everything looks good.

Mukta SemiBold Regular (Mukta-SemiBold.ttf)

name

MS NID 16/17

MS NID 16 + NID 17 should match NID 1 (+2).
Otherwise cross platform compatibility does not work between Mac (uses NID 16+17) and Windows (uses NID 1+2). (Jan 2019)

NID 16 'Mukta' + 'Space' + NID 17 'SemiBold' = NID 1 'Mukta SemiBold'.

Pass

Mukta ExtraBold Regular (Mukta-ExtraBold.ttf)

name

MS NID 16/17

MS NID 16 + NID 17 should match NID 1 (+2).
Otherwise cross platform compatibility does not work between Mac (uses NID 16+17) and Windows (uses NID 1+2). (Jan 2019)

NID 16 'Mukta' + 'Space' + NID 17 'ExtraBold' = NID 1 'Mukta ExtraBold'.

Pass

Mukta ExtraLight Regular (Mukta-ExtraLight.ttf)

post

PostScript names

Postscript names should not be longer then 29 characters. May cause issues in PDF.

Is longer:
'matraIiRephChandrabinduone.dv
matraIiRephChandrabindutwo.dv
matraShortERephChandrabindu.dv
matraShortORephChandrabindu.dv'
